      >{site['site-url'].replace('https://', '')}</a
    > at commit <a
      href=`https://github.com/jakemulley/jakemulley.github.io/commit/${commitHash}`
      >{commitHash}</a
    >.
  </p>
  <p set:html={socialParagraph} />
</footer>
